0. DEFINITIONS

"Software" means the source code, documentation, configuration files, and all
associated materials made available by TrieOH under this License.

"Run Locally" means executing the Software on a personal machine solely for
the purpose of studying or evaluating it, with no production or service use.

"Commercial Use" means any use of the Software, in whole or in part, in
connection with a product, service, or activity intended to generate revenue
or provide value to third parties.

"Contribution" means any bug report, patch, suggestion, or other submission
made to TrieOH through the official contribution channel.

"Official Contribution Channel" means the GitHub mirror repository at
https://github.com/trieoh, where issues and pull requests are accepted as
the public interface for community contributions.

